pproach has radically reduced the\nmaximum TT estimation errors to 29 hours. Previous studies determined the TT\nwith a maximum error equal to 50 hours.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Oct 2019 13:54:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-08"}
