cture interactions (e.g., transport of solid bodies\nby floods and earth landslides; rock landslides). SPHERA is developed and\ndistributed on a GitHub public repository.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Oct 2019 07:46:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-11"}
